Package: dct3-emu
Version: @VERSION@
Section: otherosfs
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libsdl2-2.0-0, libc6
Maintainer: @MAINTAINER@
Installed-Size: @ISIZE@
Description: Nokia 3310 (DCT3) firmware emulator — beta GUI
 A native SDL2 emulator of the Nokia 3310 (NHM-5, MAD2). It boots a real DCT3
 firmware image to a live LCD with keypad input, earpiece audio, on-screen power
 button, and a screenshot key.
 .
 This is a slimmed BETA build: 3310 only, with the DSP co-simulation and all
 developer/debug/tracing knobs compiled out.
 .
 Firmware is NOT included (it is copyrighted Nokia code). Supply your own 3310
 .fls dump — see /usr/share/doc/dct3-emu/README.md.
